snippet.title: Let's Play: Shooting Gallery (Magnavox Odyssey 1972)
snippet.description: Shooting Gallery is a Magnavox Odyssey game released in 1972.  It was part of a boxed set that included four games, two game cards, and a light rifle. This video was produced as part of the OdysseyNow project at the University of Pittsburgh, directed by Zachary Horton.
